      R<RpcStatus> ReleaseCollection(ReleaseCollectionParam requestParam)
      Releases the loaded collection from memory. All data in the released collection remains intact after this operation. You can load the collection to memory again using LoadCollection().
      参数:
      requestParam - A LoadCollectionParam object as the request parameter.
      返回:
      A RpcStatus object indicating whether this operation succeeds.
